WEBVTT

03:50.772 --> 03:53.483
It was good
to get a taste of home, Mama.

03:53.566 --> 03:57.612
Your sister had to go all the way
to Cefalù to send you those tomatoes.

03:57.695 --> 04:01.449
Wow, really?
They will make a delicious Sicilian pesto.

04:01.532 --> 04:04.953
How is Rosalina? And Biagia?

04:06.246 --> 04:08.039
Rosalina looks just like you at that age.

04:08.831 --> 04:10.541
Let's hope she grows out of it.

04:10.625 --> 04:12.627
You should see your father with Rosalina.

04:13.711 --> 04:15.213
And how would I do that?

04:16.506 --> 04:18.424
Did you ever tell him we met in Cefalù?

04:20.051 --> 04:22.178
That I held my niece?

04:22.262 --> 04:25.306
What he doesn't know won't hurt him.

04:25.390 --> 04:26.307
Thought so.

04:28.810 --> 04:31.813
Mama, I have to go. Bye.

10:16.824 --> 10:20.286
10, 11, 12, 13…
13 dollars for fuck's sake.

10:20.369 --> 10:22.997
Silvio, sorry I got you a job here.

10:23.080 --> 10:24.498
It's fine.

10:41.432 --> 10:43.351
Damn it!

14:24.738 --> 14:26.657
One second. One second.

14:27.658 --> 14:32.162
Mamma, I got it. I add the tomatoes,
then I add the water and the vinegar.

14:33.372 --> 14:34.206
And then?

18:03.874 --> 18:05.334
I could eat you…

18:32.236 --> 18:35.155
Thanks very much.
Very nice of you.

35:18.157 --> 35:19.700
I love you too, Mama.

35:21.577 --> 35:24.539
Bye.
